EN: This room is too dark, I can't find the switch.

ZH: 我喜欢黑咖啡，不加任何糖。
EN: I like black coffee, no sugar added.

ZH: 她的头发是黑色的，看起来很漂亮。
EN: Her hair is black and it looks very pretty.

ZH: 黑猫在夜晚特别难以发现。
EN: Black cats are especially hard to spot at night.

