EN: A dark room is full of mystery.

ZH: 黑暗中透着一丝光亮。
EN: There is a faint light shining through the darkness.

ZH: 在不公开的黑市上，各种走私商品都能找到。
EN: All kinds of smuggled goods can be found in the underground black market.

ZH: 黑客是指能够攻击电脑网络的专家。
EN: Black hat hackers are experts who can attack computer networks.

ZH: 这本书的背面是一片黑底白字的设计。
EN: The back of this book has a black background with white words.

ZH: 黑发女孩拍摄了一组时尚照片。
EN: The black-haired girl took a series of fashionable photos.

